Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.34,0:00:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, was Sasahara actually sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.01,0:00:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he totally was.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.47,0:00:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His arms were crossed and he wasn't moving at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.97,0:00:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misato, go back and wake him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.64,0:00:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasahara probably forgot\Nwe're changing classrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.77,0:00:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's it matter? Just let him be.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.98,0:00:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.35,0:00:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's your childhood friend. Go and wake him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.94,0:00:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, Sasahara is probably all alone\Nin the classroom right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.11,0:00:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.11,0:00:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.36,0:00:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go ahead without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.12,0:00:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.49,0:00:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.16,0:00:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh! Why am I the one\Nwho has to do something about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.91,0:00:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because we're childhood--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should confess to Sasahara already.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.42,0:00:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Greatest friendship{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.51,0:00:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Super duper harmony{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.18,0:00:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(na na na na na na na){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.81,0:01:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey! I'll say it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.97,0:01:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You are my best best friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.94,0:01:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(bright) Every time I poke fun and tease you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.27,0:01:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(shine) You come and tease me back some more{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.73,0:01:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(lan lan lan) There ain't\Nno better feeling in the world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.49,0:01:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(why) Even when bad things sometimes happen{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.87,0:01:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(fine) I forget all of them around you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.12,0:01:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(lan lan lan) We'll forever let the good times roll{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.62,0:01:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not a problem being with you\Nevery hour of the day{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.08,0:01:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As if we're twins, child-parent,\Nor a pair of cloned cells{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.29,0:01:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Doesn't a friendship this good\Nmake love not so needed anymore?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.75,0:01:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait hold on this and that\Nare totally totally different things{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.63,0:01:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(fight) Even after we've had a fight{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.09,0:01:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(down) Or when I feel down in the dumps{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.39,0:01:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(shock) All the times I wanted to be alone{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.85,0:01:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Before I know it there sitting beside me\Nmy wonderful friend till the end{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why is it, I wanna be at your side?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whenever we're together,\Ntime flies 100 times faster{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.73,0:01:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's so fun with you,\NI think it's almost too much fun{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.53,0:01:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's cuz you're such a good friend! Hey!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.45,0:01:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(na na na na na na na){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.24,0:02:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's going on? Uh-oh we're synchronizing man!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.32,0:02:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's always a wild time,\Nwe make the people 'round us crazy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.12,0:02:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What time is it now? I think it's yodelayheehoo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.12,0:02:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's that even mean?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.37,0:02:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}SO-RE-DO-SHI-RA-{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.12,0:02:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unbelievably, how to put it, awesome!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.58,0:02:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter what happens\Nwe are gonna be friends! Woohoo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.09,0:02:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Greatest friendship{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.09,0:02:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Super duper harmony{\i0}
