Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.65,0:02:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasahara!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.81,0:02:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're moving classrooms\Nso what are you sleeping for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misato Tachibana.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.82,0:02:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Go and get your textbook for class.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.16,0:02:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.49,0:02:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only intended to rest my eyes a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.41,0:02:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must have been lulled to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.12,0:02:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better hurry it up, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.08,0:02:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're both late to class,\Npeople will misunderstand!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.67,0:02:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misunderstand?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:02:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:02:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"My Ordinary Life 106" {\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.60,0:03:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.39,0:03:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I mean is, what was it doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault for being so slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.14,0:03:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misato Tachibana.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.10,0:03:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's blood on your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you being nice for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.24,0:03:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be angry that I broke your glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.49,0:03:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't hurt when my glasses are broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.79,0:03:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it hurts your hand, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.21,0:03:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.46,0:03:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to sound cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.34,0:03:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately, one of the lenses is still intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.39,0:03:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a fragile survivor of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.69,0:03:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of a fragile survivor...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of fragile...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.12,0:04:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll guide you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.53,0:04:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misato Tachibana.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what I did was bad... I know it's my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"As soon as they begin walking..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"As soon as they begin walking..."\NYou know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.71,0:04:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's totally not cool at--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.63,0:04:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.88,0:04:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right? But then--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! They're staring!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm dying! I'm dying!\NSo embarrassed I'm dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.85,0:04:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, it's my fault I broke his glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to act as Sasahara's eyes for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.94,0:04:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.98,0:04:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I tell people his glasses are broke,\Nthey'll see I'm just doing a good deed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! I'm just being a nice volunteer\Nby being his eyes for the whole day!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.91,0:04:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misato Tachibana.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before we go to the classroom,\NI'd like to use the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.79,0:04:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The toilet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.38,0:04:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, the men's toilet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An obstacle has appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.38,0:05:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I'm the one whose fault this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What doesn't kill you makes you stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm coming, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.56,0:05:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because your glasses are broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.73,0:05:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, are you clueless?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't see at all, so I'm saying\NI'll be your eyes for the rest of the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.61,0:05:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.94,0:05:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't misunderstand, all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There happened to be a bug on your right arm!\NI was only trying to slowly crush it with mine, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What beautiful weather today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.63,0:05:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8} "Shinonome Lab" {\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Nap" "Shinonome Lab"{\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:05:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Curry" U-Um!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.56,0:06:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Curry"\NThere's this spicy curry restaurant in Kamakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.48,0:06:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Sakurai, which level of spicy do you eat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.44,0:06:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.03,0:06:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only zero...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"My Ordinary Life 107" {\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Naganohara?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Class is about to start...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Class is about to start...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.67,0:06:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Mio! The Language Lab isn't that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Language Lab...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, hey, besides! It's like baseball,\Nyou never know what's gonna happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.56,0:06:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what makes life fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never know what's gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's baseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.60,0:06:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still don't know if that person\Nis his girlfriend, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Nano?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.40,0:06:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Ah, yeah! That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.74,0:06:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasahara is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.95,0:06:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.66,0:06:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.58,0:07:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, let's head back, Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naganohara!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nano, get to Language Lab\Nand make an excuse for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.17,0:07:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio! You'll crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.43,0:07:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.68,0:07:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.89,0:07:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio!
