Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.91,0:07:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.95,0:07:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.26,0:07:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Say cheese!\N--Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.64,0:08:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.82,0:08:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.58,0:08:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio! Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio! Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.79,0:08:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ma fell in the river!\N--Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio! Mio! Mio! Mio! Mio! Mio! Mio! Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.60,0:08:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ch-Chan Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:08:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ch-Chan Mio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.89,0:09:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.52,0:09:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.12,0:09:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm whipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.79,0:09:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.17,0:09:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.63,0:09:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.79,0:09:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Osamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.34,0:09:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:09:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because this person saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.89,0:10:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.89,0:10:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you two know that interfering\Nwith police work is a criminal offense!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two?! Even me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, I'd try to get a hold of your school, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given the circumstances, I'll overlook it this once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.57,0:10:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.70,0:10:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are. There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally tracked you down, Braid Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.75,0:10:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After seeing you shadow box...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.37,0:10:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...something sparked in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.13,0:10:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With boxing... You can take the world by storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.56,0:10:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He snatched my purse!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.52,0:10:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't think bad of me!\N--He snatched my purse!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotta go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to the station later!\NYou'll get commendation for your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, lady... Will you take this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:10:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Osamu, you don't mind right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.20,0:11:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're ready, please make a trip to the gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.49,0:11:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll talk to you then when you come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.49,0:11:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, your English textbook\Ngot lost during all of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rejected before I even confessed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.88,0:11:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saved a kid while sprinting at full speed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got an award... Got a kite...\NGot scouted by a boxer...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true. You never know what's gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's exactly how you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never know what's gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.32,0:11:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's baseball. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.86,0:11:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.66,0:11:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Word-Time" {\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.63,0:11:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just realized that daydreaming is totally free.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn... I completely lost track of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"My Ordinary Life 108"\NDamn... I completely lost track of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.65,0:12:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was right on her mark at school, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment I took my eyes off her,\Nshe suddenly disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.40,0:12:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a remarkable advanced feature.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.61,0:12:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It only makes me want to know\Nyour secrets more, Nano Shinonome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've come this far.\NPerhaps I should look for her house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,0:12:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... It may be dangerous to probe too deeply.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll continue tailing her tomorrow\Nand back out for today--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.26,0:12:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Shinonome Lab" {\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's completely in the open!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I stumbled across her house. This is my first lucky\Nbreak since beginning my mission to capture her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.43,0:12:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is more than mere luck.\NIt's what you'd call... Um, uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.48,0:12:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.61,0:13:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shinonome"\NWhat's with this rising tension?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.36,0:13:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to sneak right in and take a look at the lab!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.41,0:13:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see the person who made her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to steal her blueprints!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This excitement is causing a stampede in my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, the cowboy inside me, Bill Watts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.37,0:13:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is the house of her creator,\Nthere's no knowing what traps there may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must restrain myself to be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.21,0:13:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Today, I'll just have a peek--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.38,0:13:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.84,0:13:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guinea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! I was spotted by a surveillance robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.56,0:13:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks cheaply built, but he's probably made\Nwith the same advanced technology as Nano!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm a threat, who knows what he'll do to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.77,0:13:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, I need to appear innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.94,0:13:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Nakamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.57,0:13:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guinea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.49,0:13:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"School Counseling Office" {\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last week, I heard your goat\Ncarried a hurt old lady to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.04,0:13:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why you come to school\Non a goat, for situations like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.79,0:14:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Riding your goat is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.22,0:14:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I let down my guard and it cost me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.23,0:14:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And though I've infiltrated her house,\NI mustn't forget I'm in hostile territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make no mistake, I'm surrounded by traps.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.61,0:14:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, this tea. I'm certain\Nit contains some drug to erase my memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this room, too. It must be under surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.83,0:14:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something about it is all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.92,0:14:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sitting there so randomly, I'm almost positive\Nit's watching over my each and every move.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I do something wrong... it'll get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.47,0:14:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry! It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.93,0:14:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I drank it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Um, was it too hot?\N--How foolish of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.65,0:15:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got nothing to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come straight out and say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.07,0:15:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here because I want\Nto know everything about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.70,0:15:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.66,0:15:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to show me your true self!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Eh?!\N--No?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.66,0:15:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um! Everyone's free\Nto make their own decisions, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.08,0:15:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two girls dating isn't so normal, and I think,\Nprobably for me, that normal is best...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.47,0:15:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You dummy! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.01,0:15:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking? That's so embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.72,0:15:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.85,0:15:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I meant by knowing everything about you is--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nano?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.31,0:15:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hakase!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Eh?!\N--Hakase!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.44,0:15:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Eh?!\N--Nano...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Is this the one she calls Hakase?\N--Nano...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Is this the one she calls Hakase?\N--We ran out of snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.11,0:15:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No, no, I must've misheard something.\N--We ran out of snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No, no, I must've misheard something.\N--You'll have to wait for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No, no, I must've misheard something.\N--Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.65,0:15:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This child can't be the one\N--Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--who created Nano Shinonome.\N--Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.40,0:15:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--who created Nano Shinonome.\N--Who's this person?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.24,0:15:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Could she be one of her relatives?\N--Who's this person?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Could she be one of her relatives?\N--It's Ms. Nakamura from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.49,0:15:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Her younger sister?\N--It's Ms. Nakamura from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ah!\N--It's Ms. Nakamura from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.28,0:15:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means, the child is a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.83,0:16:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, I'm Hakase.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I created Nano.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.87,0:16:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoulder block!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.29,0:16:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--H-Hakase! Why did you say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Created? This child created Nano?\N--H-Hakase! Why did you say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Created? This child created Nano?\N--It's just my introduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.17,0:16:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.38,0:16:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do something about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.34,0:16:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That brat screwed with me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.55,0:16:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ho... Ho...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.93,0:16:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Homunculus!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The surveillance robot! The daruma weapon!\NThe child Hakase! Nano Shinonome! Homunculus!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.85,0:16:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I admit it was stupid to come into this house\Ncompletely unprepared and unarmed, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought it'd be this dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.20,0:16:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I've gotta find a chance to escape from here\N--Hakase, how did you tie this knot?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.28,0:16:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--and reformulate my plans!\N--Hakase, how did you tie this knot?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.74,0:16:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--and reformulate my plans!\N--Tighty-tight knot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.78,0:16:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--and reformulate my plans!\N--Not again, Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.87,0:16:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing that thing will attack\Nmakes me so scared I'm afraid to move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.67,0:16:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I suddenly say something like I have to go home...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.96,0:16:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This leaves just one option...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.63,0:16:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to use the toilet. Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:16:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.59,0:16:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.51,0:16:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.93,0:17:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you tell me where it is, I can go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.85,0:17:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You completely fell for it, Nano Shinonome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.73,0:17:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My escape tactic has worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it would. She believed I'd do\Nexactly what I said I'd do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.24,0:17:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Her weakness is that she trusts people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.62,0:17:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next time I come back to this place,\NI'll be turning the tables on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.29,0:17:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.58,0:17:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you still have that weak point,\NI'll come back as much as it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.63,0:17:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Were you leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.05,0:17:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.09,0:17:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.38,0:17:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well... I was asked to\Ntake care of the grass outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.47,0:17:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, don't move an inch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! They're onto me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.56,0:17:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all going to find out\NI was trying to sneak away and escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! What is this stuff?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.15,0:17:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body! My freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:17:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:18:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? The toilet's not that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ack! What in the world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.62,0:18:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.83,0:18:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakase! Doesn't this glue come off with water?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--If they capture me here, it's all over for me.\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--If they capture me here, it's all over for me.\N--Water! Water!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--All my hopes! All my dreams!\N--Water! Water!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--All my hopes! All my dreams!\N--Huh? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Crap! I've got to get out of here somehow!\N--Huh? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Crap! I've got to get out of here somehow!\N--I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.47,0:18:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You bastards from the Shinonome Lab!\N--Hurry up and take this off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.22,0:18:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You bastards from the Shinonome Lab!\N--Nano! I want snacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Water! Water!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.01,0:18:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Someone help me...\N--Water! Water!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Someone help me...\N--What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Someone help me...\N--Nano!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.39,0:18:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Anyone!\N--Nano!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.43,0:18:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Anyone!\N--Bring water!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.85,0:18:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Somebody help me!\N--Bring water!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"No Eternal Life No Killing" {\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:18:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"My Ordinary Life 109"\NOh, I actually have that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.63,0:19:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"My Ordinary Life 109"\NReally? Could I borrow it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Could I borrow it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.97,0:19:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. I'll bring it next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.35,0:19:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never know what's\Ngonna happen. That's baseball...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.23,0:19:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all she said?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.73,0:19:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. And then she laughed and acted all happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.52,0:19:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think she's just pretending?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was kinda rejected by\Nthe guy she's liked for so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.61,0:19:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't not look like she's not happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.32,0:19:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, which was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.58,0:19:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko, did you forget your homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.91,0:19:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, but you're right,\NI did forget my homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.33,0:19:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.08,0:19:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer... is after the commercials!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.38,0:19:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.59,0:19:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so funny, Aioi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.42,0:19:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Minakami?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.59,0:19:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Left-hand rule?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.59,0:19:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rap?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.43,0:19:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naganohara. There's something else I need to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.56,0:19:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.89,0:19:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aioi, is there anything you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some way to cheer up Naganohara.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why they all left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was hoping to grab a bite\Nwith Yuuko and the others, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.75,0:20:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.04,0:20:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a spin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? That's Yuuko, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko? Who might that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.01,0:20:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's totally obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.64,0:20:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can even see Nano's key.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.39,0:20:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This isn't anything robotic!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.06,0:20:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, everyone who comes\Nthrough here has to do the lottery.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.14,0:20:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Hurry, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.35,0:20:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get what this is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.82,0:20:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just turn it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.11,0:20:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're so loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.28,0:20:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your special prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.41,0:20:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just take it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.37,0:20:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I keep telling you that these\Nlittle jokes of yours are so annoy--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.93,0:21:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great, now go on your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.22,0:21:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.85,0:21:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bonus prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.15,0:21:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Freshly carved.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.15,0:21:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.25,0:21:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard once that Sasahara said\Nsomething a while back...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.46,0:21:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That our ordinary lives that pass by day by day...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.59,0:21:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...actually may be a series of wonderful miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.47,0:21:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think... No, I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.93,0:21:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.90,0:22:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Friends for life coupon"\N"Aioi" "Shinonome" "Minakami"{\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.65,0:22:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Aioi" "Shinonome" "Minakami"{\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.58,0:22:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's go home and draw manga!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.36,0:23:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's search for tomorrow in this huge world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.21,0:23:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now is the time, so let's all journey together{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.14,0:23:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Towards tomorrow's endless possibilities{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.02,0:23:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Finding all of our hopes and our dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.53,0:23:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's search for tomorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.33,0:23:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Search for tomorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.63,0:23:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's search for tomorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.22,0:23:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In this huge world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.72,0:24:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In this huge world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.57,0:24:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Love-Like" {\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.57,0:24:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh. It's your fault we got lost out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.61,0:24:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I'll look up the way on my mobile phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.70,0:24:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, do you think you're British?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.33,0:24:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just call it a cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.16,0:24:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.41,0:24:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you watching TV on there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.58,0:24:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misato Tachibana should watch TV on hers, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.34,0:24:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine doesn't have TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.22,0:24:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Nano's Key!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.85,0:24:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes I spin, sometimes I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.06,0:24:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes I get pulled out! That's my daily life!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.52,0:24:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The next {\i1}My Ordinary Life {\i0}is the last!{\an}
